description: ConfiguredGrant: This table stores configuration details for granted resources in a radio access network,  specifically focusing on Ericsson-specific attributes.  Columns include timestamp (dateTime), geographic location (Area_Name), cell identifiers (CellId, Id2),  additional identifiers (Id3, Id4), data type identifier (vsDataType), data format version (vsDataFormatVersion), and a unique grant ID (ConfiguredGrant.configuredGrantId).
